    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm not against the idea of flattening the release notes into a text file. However, we've typically done the notes so far after the release has been done. Making sure everything is in sync with a changelog file would significantly slow down our release process, which is already a tad bit too slow for our taste."
