    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "That's certainly a fair point in theory, but a very hard aspiration to live up to in practice -- particularly when trying to support such a large number of languages simultaneously. I would encourage you to take advantage of your community in the course of identifying these very scenarios by better empowering them to help identify the sources of bugs as they are introduced. I think I'll leave it at that."
